data.description:
Back on market at no fault of the seller-previous buyer lost job and financing 1 week before closing.
Stunning END unit townhome featuring a primary bedroom on the main floor! With a brand new AC unit installed in July 2023 & new vinyl plank flooring on 1st floor. The Great Room has magnificent vaulted ceilings that fill the space with an abundance of natural light. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, beautiful granite countertops, white cabinets, & breakfast bar. The primary bedroom on the main floor is both spacious and inviting, equipped with double closets for ample storage. The en-suite bath has been remodeled with a new walk-in shower installed. Upstairs, you'll discover two generously sized bedrooms, one with a HUGE walk-in closet.  New sliding glass doors installed on tub in the full bath on the 2nd level ensures comfort and convenience. Situated in a prime location,  close to shopping centers, a variety of dining options, and provides easy access to the nearby I-77.
